race.comment: CHEERFUL COW (3) could manage only eighth after making contact in the run last time in a Grade 5 at Goulburn, finishing 9 lengths from the winner (20.84). Better than last start and worth following up. ACE DIVA (4) steps out for the first time at this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 7 lengths (18.99) at Q Straight. The form out of last race has been strong. Great chance to atone. SPIRIT CHANA (1) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at this track over 340m behind DAMAGED PANEL (20.57) in a Grade 4. The form out of her last race has been franked. Better than last start and can bounce back. JOHN'S PROMISE (2) is likely to have admirers.
